name: KastanDay/notes_enhancer
description: Mission statement:   1. Find "unlinked mentions" between pages via semantic search. As a page is written, the rest of your notes are 'fuzzy' searched for synonymous (and opposite) terms, people. 2. Use content generation to "finish your thought" and extend your notes to make them more rich and searchable. 3. Search the web (Wikipedia, Google knowledge graph) for topics & people mentioned in your notes. Append that content to the bottom of your notes to make notes richer, and easily searchable. This is a positive feedback loop that helps make more connections between notes, as well.
